# Building Custom AI Assistants and AI Support with Theia AI

## Overview

Theia AI is a framework designed to help tool builders integrate tailored AI capabilities into their tools and IDEs. This documentation targets developers using Theia and Theia AI as a platform to build custom tools and IDEs.

